      "markText": "阿保正将他的手放到新城乔子的肩膀上。",
      "totalCount": 1072,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020507&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5170&rangeEnd=5188",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3e322a0813ab6e82g017293?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5170&rangeEnd=5188"
