    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020507_12_1078-1101",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1078-1101",
      "markText": "“我知道，你赶快说吧。我可没有那么多闲工夫。”",
      "totalCount": 525,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020507&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1078&rangeEnd=1101",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3e322a0813ab6e82g017293?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1078&rangeEnd=1101"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020507_7_8996-9044",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8996-9044",
      "markText": "因为那不是她一个人的错，现代社会的信用卡贷款等制度，在某些意义上简直就是一种公害。”沟口继续说。",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020507&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8996&rangeEnd=9044",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3e322a0813ab6e82g017293?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8996&rangeEnd=9044"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020507_15_4111-4149",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "4111-4149",
      "markText": "人们对于随时可以买来新的替换的东西是没有归属感的，不会将这样的东西称为故乡。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020507&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4111&rangeEnd=4149",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3e322a0813ab6e82g017293?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4111&rangeEnd=4149"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020507_16_917-960",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "917-960",
      "markText": "不过，在公共场所使用手机打电话的人，为什么刚好都声音很大，而且都长着一副欠揍的样子呢？",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020507&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=917&rangeEnd=960",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3e322a0813ab6e82g017293?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=917&rangeEnd=960"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020507_7_11358-11447",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "11358-11447",
      "markText": "沟口慢慢地摇头，好像手中拿的是什么脏东西似的将履历表交还给本间，说：“这个女子和我知道的关根彰子并非同一人。我没见过她。我不知道她是谁，但我肯定她不是关根彰子。你说的是别的人。”",
      "totalCount": 464,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020507&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11358&rangeEnd=11447",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3e322a0813ab6e82g017293?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11358&rangeEnd=11447"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020507_19_8640-8679",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "8640-8679",
      "markText": "“她回答：‘这种素怎么不第一个来问偶呢？’我说的也许不算是正确的大阪口音吧。”",
      "totalCount": 448,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020507&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=8640&rangeEnd=8679",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3e322a0813ab6e82g017293?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=8640&rangeEnd=8679"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020507_16_7564-7663",
